in secret because of you.

60
00:04:16,829 --> 00:04:18,190
He's drunk. Don't listen to him.

61
00:04:18,190 --> 00:04:19,540
No!

62
00:04:19,910 --> 00:04:20,870
I have evidence.

63
00:04:21,990 --> 00:04:23,470
Let me show you

