195
00:11:53,030 --> 00:11:54,150
Let's go.

196
00:11:57,710 --> 00:11:58,780
Why should I go?

197
00:11:59,750 --> 00:12:00,830
Let's announce

198
00:12:00,830 --> 00:12:02,630
