244
00:14:24,430 --> 00:14:25,270
[I have a gift ready for you]

245
00:14:25,270 --> 00:14:27,190
[in a few days.]

246
00:14:27,390 --> 00:14:28,870
Just wait for it, okay?

247
00:14:30,430 --> 00:14:32,150
